project_description: Project by Joshua Grinham started in 2018 to collect out-of-phase magnetic susceptibility data using the AGICO KLY5-A Kappabridge from a variety of samples and mineral standards.
Oliver Dixon; 2018. Characterising the magnetic properties of molydenum.
M3ORE Laboratory; 2018. Mineral standards collected for creating standard datasets in the University of St. Andrews Rock Magnetics Laboratory.
